1470
01:42:40,039 --> 01:42:41,446
Mrs. Croft.

1471
01:42:42,471 --> 01:42:44,512
Sim, encontrei-me com ela na Regent Street.

1472
01:42:44,512 --> 01:42:46,373
Você o quê?

